 bots←Move bots;rad;alive
⍝ Move all alive bots based on their direction and speed
⍝ Clamp to arena bounds accounting for hitbox radius
 ⎕IO←0
 alive←bots[;7]
 rad←(○÷180)×bots[;3]
 bots[;1]+←alive×##.Cfg.BOT_SPEED×1○rad
 bots[;2]+←alive×##.Cfg.BOT_SPEED×2○rad
 ⍝ Clamp to arena bounds
 bots[;1]⌈←##.Cfg.BOT_RADIUS
 bots[;1]⌊←(⊃##.Cfg.ARENA)-##.Cfg.BOT_RADIUS
 bots[;2]⌈←##.Cfg.BOT_RADIUS
 bots[;2]⌊←(⊃⌽##.Cfg.ARENA)-##.Cfg.BOT_RADIUS
